Class BulkBarcodeConfigController

java.lang.Object
com.agaramtech.qualis.restcontroller.BulkBarcodeConfigController
@RestController @RequestMapping("/bulkbarcodeconfiguration") public class BulkBarcodeConfigController extends Object
This controller is used to dispatch the input request to its relevant method to access the Bulk Barcode Config Service methods
